<h1>Where to Give</h1>
<div class="intro">
  <p>UCI&#8217;s&#160;unyielding commitment to teaching, research and public service makes the campus a driving force for innovation and discovery that serves our local, national and global communities in many ways. You have thousands of choices of where to give that will make a meaningful impact on the students, scientists, faculty and the future.</p>
<h2>Support one of the areas below or <a href="https://secure.connect.uci.edu/s/1735/interior-1col.aspx?sid=1735&amp;gid=3&amp;pgid=801&amp;cid=1850" target="_blank">find an area that matters most to you </a><a href="https://secure.connect.uci.edu/s/1735/interior-1col.aspx?sid=1735&amp;gid=3&amp;pgid=801&amp;cid=1850" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">&#187;</a></h2>
</div>
<div class="buckets">
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">UCI Fund</h2>
            <a href="/UCIFund/index.php"><img alt="Where to Give: The UCI Fund" src="/img/schools/UCI_Fund.jpg"/></a>
            <p>The UCI Fund provides the university with the flexibility to support the great, emerging needs and opportunities on campus. Your gift of any size is not only a vote of confidence in UCI&#8217;s excellent work but also an investment in California&#8217;s future.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">UCI Health</h2>
            <a href="http://www.ucirvinehealth.org/giving/"><img alt="Where to Give: UCI Health" src="/img/give/where_to_give_uci_medical_center_640x360.jpg"/></a>
            <p>When you make a gift to UCI Health, the only academic medical system in the region, the full 100 percent goes to support programs and services that save and transform lives.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Alumni Association</h2>
            <a href="http://alumni.uci.edu/give/index.php"><img alt="Where to Give: UCI Alumni Association" src="/img/give/where_to_give_alumni.jpg"/></a>
            <p>For nearly 50 years, the UCI Alumni Association has prioritized enriching the lives of alumni and engaging them in the lifelong advancement of their alma mater.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Schools</h2>
            <a href="/give/schools/index.php"><img alt="Where to Give: Schools" src="/img/give/where_to_give_schools_and_units_640x360.jpg"/></a>
            <p>By supporting one of the schools on campus, you are advancing academic discovery and changing the lives of our talented UCI students.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Athletics</h2>
            <a href="http://give.uci.edu/give/schools/athletics.php"><img alt="Where to Give: Athletics" src="/img/give/where_to_give_uci_athletics_2_640x360.jpg"/></a>
            <p>Your support helps maintain not only the highest standards of excellence in competition and sportsmanship but also enhances the athletic facilities that maximize athletic performance.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Campus Programs</h2>
            <a href="/give/campus-programs/index.php"><img alt="Where to Give: Campus Programs" src="/img/give/where_to_give_campus_programs_640x360.jpg"/></a>
            <p>By supporting one of our campus programs, you are helping create the opportunities that will ensure our students&#8217; future success.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Chancellorâ€™s Club</h2>
            <a href="/UCIFund/Chancellors-Club/index.php"><img alt="UCI Chancellorâ€™s Club" src="/img/give/where_to_give_chancellors_club.jpg"/></a>
            <p>Chancellor&#8217;s Club gifts support the areas of critical need as determined by the chancellor.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Civil and Environmental Engineering Affiliates</h2>
            <a href="/give/cee.php"><img alt="Engineering Hall" src="/img/give/support-groups/cee-640.jpg"/></a>
            <p>By joining the UCI Civil and Environmental Engineering Affiliates, you are offering support and guidance to not only the Department of Civil and Environmental Engineering at UCI but also its programs and students.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Class Reunions</h2>
            <a href="http://engage.alumni.uci.edu/s/1735/alumni/index1col.aspx?sid=1735&amp;gid=2&amp;pgid=1863"><img alt="UCI Class Reunions" src="/img/give/where_to_give_class_-reunions.jpg"/></a>
            <p>By contributing to your reunion class gift, you are supplying UCI with the strength and stability to remain one of the best universities in the country.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Foundersâ€™ Pledge</h2>
            <a href="/give/founders-pledge/index.php"><img alt="Foundersâ€™ Pledge" src="/give/founders-pledge/img/Founders-Pledge1.jpg"/></a>
            <p>Show your Anteater pride and leave your legacy on our world-renowned university by signing the UCI Founders&#8217; Pledge.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Legacy Society</h2>
            <a href="http://www.plannedgiving.uci.edu/?pageID=1003"><img alt="UCI Legacy Society" src="/img/give/where_to_give_legacy_society"/></a>
            <p>Gifts made by our Legacy Society members ensure that UCI remains on the cutting-edge of education and research for generations to come.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Parent Campaign for Student Success</h2>
            <a href="/UCIFund/Parents-Program/index.php"><img alt="UCI Parent Engagement" src="/img/give/chancellors-club/where_to_give_parent_engagement.jpg"/></a>
            <p>By giving to the UCI Parent Campaign for Student Success, you are directly impacting every student on campus.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Research Associates</h2>
            <a href="/give/research-associates.php"><img alt="Medical Students" src="/img/give/support-groups/research-associates-640.jpg"/></a>
            <p>Every year, this organization focuses on a specific fundraising effort that will support an outstanding researcher at UCI&#8217;s School of Medicine.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Research Centers &amp; Institutes</h2>
            <a href="/give/research-centers-and-institutes/index.php"><img alt="Where to Give: Research Centers &amp; Institutes" src="/img/give/where_to_give_the_research_centers_640x360.jpg"/></a>
            <p>Discovery and innovation are in our DNA here at UCI. With your support, we will continue to advance groundbreaking solutions to our world&#8217;s grand challenges.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Scholarships &amp; Fellowships</h2>
            <a href="/give/scholarships-and-fellowships/index.php"><img alt="Where to Give: Scholarships &amp; Fellowships" src="/img/give/where_to_give_the_scholorships.jpg"/></a>
            <p>Of all the philanthropic gifts one can bestow upon a university, there is perhaps no gift with a greater or more immediate impact for students than scholarships and fellowships.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Senior Class Gift</h2>
            <a href="http://connect.uci.edu/s/1735/interior2.aspx?sid=1735&amp;gid=3&amp;pgid=2423"><img alt="UCI Senior Class Gift" src="/img/give/where_to_give_senior_class_gift.jpg"/></a>
            <p>Through the Senior Class Gift campaign, seniors are able to have a lasting impression on UCI and future Anteaters.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">Staff and Faculty Program</h2>
            <a href="/UCIFund/Staff-and-Faculty/index.php"><img alt="UCI Staff and Faculty Program" src="/img/give/where_to_give_staff_and_faculty.jpg"/></a>
            <p>Whether you are part of our world-class faculty or excellent staff, you have an opportunity to make an even greater impact by giving through the UCI faculty and staff program.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">UCI Town and Gown</h2>
            <a href="/give/support-groups/town-and-gown.php"><img alt="Humanities bridge" src="/img/give/support-groups/town-and-gown-640.jpg"/></a>
            <p>For more than 50 years, the UCI Town and Gown has been supporting students and programs at UCI. Membership and participation in this group makes its scholarships possible.</p>
    </div>
              <div class="bucket">
      <h2 class="bucket-header">ZotFunder</h2>
            <a href="https://zotfunder.give.uci.edu/"><img alt="UCI Crowdfunding" src="/img/give/ZotFunder.jpg"/></a>
            <p>Join UCI students, faculty and friends to transform bright ideas into game-changing realities.</p>
    </div>
